  .project-name GuestGuru
  .project-description
    p.
      GuestGuru introduces a new way to communicate between guests and hotel managers.
    p.
      Guests can use their favorite messengers to report an issue, send a request, or leave a feedback.
    p.
      Hotel managers can see all the messages categorized and sorted on the solid dashboard.
    p.
      This service has been being made during the AccorHotels Hackathon in 24h. Facebook Messenger and Telegram bots supported.
